==English==

===Etymology===
Named after the logician [[w:Haskell Curry|Haskell Curry]]

===Proper noun===
'''Haskell'''

# A type of [[functional]] [[programming language]] with features such as support for [[recursive]] functions and [[pattern-matching]].
# (''used [[attributively]]'') Of or relating to Haskell.
# (''used [[attributively]]'') Of a program, etc, written in Haskell.

